TITLE: tRPC Authorization Using Middleware
DESCRIPTION: Implementation of authorization using tRPC middleware, creating a reusable protected procedure that can be applied to multiple endpoints.
SOURCE: https://github.com/trpc/trpc/blob/main/www/docs/server/authorization.md#2025-04-23_snippet_2

