TITLE: Recursively Decorating a tRPC Router Structure
DESCRIPTION: Defines a recursive type that traverses a tRPC router structure and applies the procedure decorator to each procedure, maintaining the structure of routers and sub-routers.
SOURCE: https://github.com/trpc/trpc/blob/main/www/blog/2023-01-17-tinyrpc-client.mdx#2025-04-23_snippet_4

LANGUAGE: typescript
CODE:
```
import type { TRPCRouterRecord } from "@trpc/server";
import type { AnyTRPCRouter } from "@trpc/server";

type DecorateRouterRecord<TRecord extends TRPCRouterRecord> = {
  [TKey in keyof TRecord]: TRecord[TKey] extends infer $Value
    ? $Value extends TRPCRouterRecord
      ? DecorateRouterRecord<$Value>
      : $Value extends AnyTRPCProcedure
      ? DecorateProcedure<$Value>
      : never
    : never;
};
```

