TITLE: Configuring SSE Stream Producer Options for tRPC Server
DESCRIPTION: This interface defines the options for configuring the Server-Sent Events (SSE) stream producer on the server side. It includes settings for ping intervals, maximum duration, immediate ending, and client-specific options like reconnection timing.
