TITLE: Defining tRPC AppRouter in TypeScript
DESCRIPTION: This snippet defines a tRPC AppRouter with procedures for listing, retrieving, and creating posts. It uses Zod for input validation and demonstrates query and mutation handlers.
SOURCE: https://github.com/trpc/trpc/blob/main/www/versioned_docs/version-10.x/client/vanilla/infer-types.md#2025-04-23_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: typescript
