TITLE: Original tRPC Router Type Implementation
DESCRIPTION: Shows the initial implementation of V10Router and MigrateV9Router types that caused performance issues due to combining v9 and v10 procedures in a single record field.
SOURCE: https://github.com/trpc/trpc/blob/main/www/blog/2023-01-14-typescript-performance-lessons.mdx#2025-04-23_snippet_3

LANGUAGE: typescript
CODE:
```
export type V10Router<TProcedureRecord> = {
  record: TProcedureRecord;
};

// convert a v9 interop router to a v10 router
export type MigrateV9Router<TV9Router extends V9Router> = V10Router<{
  [TKey in keyof TV9Router['procedures']]: MigrateProcedure<
    TV9Router['procedures'][TKey]
  > &
    LegacyV9ProcedureTag;
}>;
```

